Asset Coverage View

Discover how you can manage entitled services more efficiently with the Asset Coverage View.

Provision Entitlements with Precision
Eliminate discrepancies and minimize costly errors when managing entitlements for contracts, warranties, and maintenance plans. The Entitlements view provides agents with an overview of a customer’s entitled services, making it easier to identify what was consumed versus what was promised. Previously, entitlement information was available only in related lists, which made it difficult to discern what was available to the customer.
